posting_body: ['*** PRIME MID-WILSHIRE LOCATION!', "TWO MILES FROM THE HISTORIC GROVE AT FARMERS MARKET, THE MELROSE AVENUE SHOPPING DISTRICT, AND THE BEVERLY CENTER, LA'S PREMIER FOOD, FASHION, AND SHOPPING DESTINATION.", '***', 'Your Villa Vicente key opens more than the door to your home.', 'It uncovers a tropical paradise.', 'Escape to a four-acre residential resort surrounded by the calming sounds of fountains and gentle streams.', 'Our community of apartment homes features well-appointed units in a beautiful tropical courtyard setting.', 'This gated community is professionally managed with excellent management and maintenance staff.', 'Ideally located near a plethora of shopping, dining and entertainment options, our Los Angeles rental homes offer air conditioning, mirrored closets, and balconies or patios in most units.', 'Visit our residential community and discover tranquil living and big city convenience.', '- Studio and one-bedroom layouts', '- Mirrored oversized closets', '- Internet café', '- Gated community', '- Nightly courtesy patrol', '- Heated resort-style swimming pool w/free wi-fi', '- Minutes to The Original Farmer’s Market', '- Hardwood-style flooring', '- 24-hour emergency on-call maintenance', '- Lush green courtyards tropical mature landscape', '- Complete stainless-steel appliance package with gas range', '- Refrigerator & microwave', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
